<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>oncofind Report — {{ cancer_type }}</title>
    <!-- Premium Typography -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Plotly CDN (required to render embedded plots) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.plotly.com/plotly-latest.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4F46E5;
            --primary-hover: #4338CA;
            --background: #F9FAFB;
            --surface: #FFFFFF;
            --text: #111827;
            --text-secondary: #4B5563;
            --border: #E5E7EB;
            --success: #10B981;
            --warning: #F59E0B;
            --danger: #EF4444;
            --shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Header Card */
        .header-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E1B4B 0%, #312E81 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -20%;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
        }

        .header-tagline {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: #A5B4FC;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .header-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .meta-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .meta-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .meta-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: #C7D2FE;
        }

        .meta-value {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Section Cards */
        .card {
            background-color: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--background);
            color: #1F2937;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        /* Plot Containers */
        .plot-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 550px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .plot-container > div {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        /* Tables */
        .table-responsive {
            width: 100%;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        td {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text);
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        tr:hover td {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
        }

        /* Badges */
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .badge-up {
            background-color: #FEE2E2;
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        .badge-down {
            background-color: #DBEAFE;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .badge-ns {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .badge-druggable {
            background-color: #D1FAE5;
            color: #065F46;
            border: 1px solid #A7F3D0;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            cursor: help;
        }

        /* Methodology */
        .method-block {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .method-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header-card">
        <div class="header-tagline">Pan-Cancer Biomarker Discovery CLI</div>
        <h1 class="header-title">Oncofind Analysis Report</h1>
        
        <div class="meta-grid">
            <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Cancer Cohort</span>
                <span class="meta-value">TCGA-{{ cancer_type | upper }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Comparison Groupby</span>
                <span class="meta-value">{{ groupby }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Group A (vs B)</span>
                <span class="meta-value">{{ group_a_val }} (N={{ n_group_a }})</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Group B (vs A)</span>
                <span class="meta-value">{{ group_b_val }} (N={{ n_group_b }})</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">DEG Method</span>
                <span class="meta-value">{{ method | upper }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Plots section -->
    {% if volcano_html %}
    <section class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Volcano Plot <span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Differential Expression Significance</span></h2>
        <div class="plot-container">
            {{ volcano_html | safe }}
        </div>
    </section>
    {% endif %}

    {% if heatmap_html %}
    <section class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Expression Heatmap <span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Top Differentially Expressed Genes (Row Z-Scores)</span></h2>
        <div class="plot-container">
            {{ heatmap_html | safe }}
        </div>
    </section>
    {% endif %}

    <!-- Top Genes Table -->
    <section class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Top Differentially Expressed Genes</h2>
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Gene</th>
                        <th>Log2 Fold Change</th>
                        <th>P-Value</th>
                        <th>Adjusted P-Value (FDR)</th>
                        <th>Direction</th>
                        <th>Targetable Therapy</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for gene in top_degs %}
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>{{ gene.gene_symbol }}</strong></td>
                        <td style="color: {% if gene.log2FC > 0 %}var(--danger){% else %}var(--primary){% endif %}; font-weight: 500;">
                            {{ "%.4f" | format(gene.log2FC) }}
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ "%.4e" | format(gene.pvalue) }}</td>
                        <td>{{ "%.4e" | format(gene.padj) }}</td>
                        <td>
                            {% if gene.padj < fdr_threshold and gene.log2FC >= fc_threshold %}
                            <span class="badge badge-up">UP</span>
                            {% elif gene.padj < fdr_threshold and gene.log2FC <= -fc_threshold %}
                            <span class="badge badge-down">DOWN</span>
                            {% else %}
                            <span class="badge badge-ns">NS</span>
                            {% endif %}
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            {% if gene.is_druggable %}
                            <span class="badge badge-druggable" title="FDA target for: {{ gene.drugs | join(', ') }}">
                                Yes ({{ gene.drugs | join(', ') }})
                            </span>
                            {% else %}
                            <span style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem;">No known drugs</span>
                            {% endif %}
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Methodology Notes -->
    {% if include_methods %}
    <section class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Methodology Notes</h2>
        <div class="method-block">
            <div class="method-title">Differential Expression Analysis</div>
            <p>
                RNA-seq count matrices are queried from the DuckDB + Parquet local database.
                Counts are normalized for sequencing library depth (CPM) or processed using PyDESeq2's negative binomial Generalized Linear Model.
                If PyDESeq2 convergence fails or sample size is small, a fallback Welch's t-test on log-transformed counts is performed.
                P-values are adjusted for multiple testing using the Benjamini-Hochberg (FDR) procedure.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="method-block">
            <div class="method-title">Batch Correction (Location-Scale Standardization)</div>
            <p>
                If multiple sequencing plates or batches are identified in clinical metadata, 
                a location-and-scale batch standardization is applied to prevent batch artifacts from skewing results.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="method-block">
            <div class="method-title">Cross-Cancer Consistency Score (CCCS)</div>
            <p>
                For pan-cancer gene validation, the CCCS combines Directionality (w=0.25), Fold Change Magnitude (w=0.25), Survival Significance (w=0.35), and Statistical Significance (w=0.15).
                Scores are scaled by the consistency ratio of significant cancer types.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    {% endif %}

    <footer>
        <p>Report generated by <strong>oncofind</strong> v0.1.0 • Running Python • MIT License</p>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
